Kumba Iron Ore Workers Will Protest Over Safety Tomorrow, Labor Union Says

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-08-12T10:45:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-12/kumba-iron-ore-workers-will-protest-over-safety-tomorrow-labor-union-says.html
Kumba Iron Ore Ltd. (KIO)  workers will
march in  South Africa ’s Northern Cape province tomorrow to
protest over safety issues, the  National Union of Mineworkers 
said in an e-mailed statement today.  “This is part of the build-up towards the national day of
mourning which will be held on Oct. 4 where mineworkers will
down tools in pursuit of their demand to be safe,” the union
said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  